You do have to seed, you know.
Right now there are more than 40 people on this, all at 0 percent. For such a small file you should have already seeded it completely and been on your way.

Okay, give it up people. This guy isn't seeding. All peers are still sitting at 0 percent. If he was going to seed this *huge* 2.42 MiB file it would have been done in the time it has taken me to enter this comment. In other words, "Move along! Nothing to see here."
What a twat. ah well, cant expect everyone to know what theyre doing...
